            "title": "3月期指低开302点报24549点",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    3月期指低开302点，报24549点；4月期指低开383点，报24447点。</span>\n</div>",
